 * Prisma Database Schema
 * 
 * Purpose: Database schema for issuer backend
 * 
 * Contains:
 * - Data source configuration (PostgreSQL/SQLite)
 * - Generator configuration (Prisma Client)
 * - Model definitions
 * 
 * Models:
 * 
 * Application:
 * - id: String @id @default(cuid())
 * - aadhaarHash: String @unique (SHA-256 of Aadhaar)
 * - holderDID: String
 * - status: String (pending, approved, rejected)
 * - livenessScore: Float
 * - createdAt: DateTime @default(now())
 * - updatedAt: DateTime @updatedAt
 * 
 * VCMetadata:
 * - id: String @id @default(cuid())
 * - vcHash: String @unique (hash of VC)
 * - cid: String (IPFS CID)
 * - holderDID: String
 * - issuedAt: DateTime @default(now())
 * - revokedAt: DateTime?
 * - blockchainTxHash: String?
 * 
 * RevocationList (Optional):
 * - id: String @id
 * - vcHash: String @unique
 * - reason: String
 * - revokedAt: DateTime @default(now())
 * 
 * Indexes:
 * - @@index([holderDID])
 * - @@index([aadhaarHash])
 * - @@index([vcHash])
 * 
 * Uses:
 * - Prisma ORM
 */
